title: Cash and Cari
overview: With her razor sharp business sense and an eye for spotting diamonds in the rough, estate sale guru Cari Cucksey combs through her clients basements, attics, and garages in search of hidden treasure. And once her team has organized and priced the entire contents of the home, they hold an estate sale right on the premises. From antique furniture and vintage toys, to retro electronics and rare cars, theres something for everyone, and everything must go!
